<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA614_03_IH_0001_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema614_01.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ena614_03">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1_green" lang="y"><span class="nemo"></span><span lang="y">안에 알맞은 말이나 수를 써넣으세요.</span></h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1 on">
          <div class="flex justify_center">
            <h3 lang="y">
              <span>한 양을 기준으로 다른 양이 몇 배가 되는지 비교하기 위해 기호 :을 사용하여 나타낸 것을</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="비"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>(이)라고 합니다.</span>
            </h3>
          </div>
          <!-- 해설 -->
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve"></div>
                <h3>한 양을 기준으로 다른 양이 몇 배가 되는지 비 교하기 위해 기호 :을 사용하여 나타낸 것을 비 라고 합니다.</h3>
              </div>

              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="btn_area">
            <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
            <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
            <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_2">
          <div class="flex justify_center">
            <h3 lang="y">
              <span>비 2 : 7에서 기준량은</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="7"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>이고, 비교하는 양은</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>입니다.</span>
            </h3>
          </div>
          <!-- 해설 -->
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve"></div>
                <h3>비 2:7에서 기준량은 7이고, 비교하는 양은 2입니다.</h3>
              </div>

              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="btn_area">
            <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
            <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
            <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
